         <div type="translation">
            <p>The Council and the People honoured with the highest and finest honours Apphia daughter of Theodoros Meliton the son of Meliton, high priestess for life of the divine Augusti and priestess of Artemis, wife of Apollonios son of Athenagoras the son of Eumachos, <seg cert="low">who also</seg>
               <gap reason="lost" unit="character" extent="unknown"/>
            </p>
         </div>
         <div type="commentary">
            <p>Discussed by Reynolds, 'The first known Aphrodisian to hold a procuratorship', (see bibliography).</p>
         </div>
